to "Report of Management" and "Report of Independent Registered Public Accounting Firm" on pages&nbsp;58 and 59 of IBM's 2008 Annual Report to Stockholders, which are
incorporated herein by reference. There has been no change in the company's internal control over financial reporting that occurred during the fourth fiscal quarter that has materially affected, or is
reasonably likely to material affect, the company's internal control over financial reporting. </FONT></P>


